  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this randomised intervention study is to investigate to what degree patients
      with colorectal cancer benefit of dietary counselling regarding nutritional status, oncologic
      treatment and quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
